Detailed Description

Declaration of AMS_5600 class.

File provides the declaration of the AMS_5600 class for reading from the AS5600 magnetic encoder on the Raspberry Pi.

The original version (written for Arduino) can be found at: https://github.com/Seeed-Studio/Seeed_Arduino_AS5600

Requires i2c-tools, libi2c-dev.
